title: Pokemon Battleground
description: React, Redux based Multiplayer online game that uses NodeJS as backend and Socket API for Real-Time Communication and data sharing. On generating a unique link 2 players can join the room and play the game.

title: Automation Builder
description: React Flow Automation Builder! This project leverages the power of React and React Flow to provide a visual and intuitive interface for creating automation workflows. Whether you're looking to simulate complex data transformations or simple input-output operations, this application offers a versatile platform to connect and configure various nodes seamlessly.
